{"tid":301433,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺街有女仔問我借電話","createTime":"2017-06-28T15:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T15:49:55.000Z","uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb3a566e6e58b83f17daff0511af34b460c078e","tid":301433,"uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"話説啱先喺街行行下<br />\n有個女仔無啦啦同我講嘢<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳<br />\n但我又帶住耳機<br />\n聽唔清佢講咩<br />\n凈係聽到&ldquo;可唔可以借個電話俾我打呀&rdquo;<br />\n咁我趕時間<br />\n凈係講句&ldquo;我冇帶電話呀&rdquo;<br />\n就走咗去<br />\n<br />\n問下各位巴打<br />\n如果喺街有陌生人問你借電話<br />\n你會唔會借？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：附近冇電話亭"},{"pid":"80fe2cc27aab33b7ad696e1f4dcce0a3742031c1","tid":301433,"uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔借"},{"pid":"7f32ac08526a07a5cf3e0f2d03dc03efca004239","tid":301433,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"可以試下同佢講<br />\n借借借 借你個閪呀！<br />\n可能即刻有女屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過記住洗返乾淨還畀人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be792b346d463898766ed95c21a5cdbdd0735691","tid":301433,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"密碼係個心"},{"pid":"be7582c6d4f71424e38655673cd60574ae829f8c","tid":301433,"uid":71458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"密碼係個心呀"},{"pid":"bd2b5994c8f519256adf3ace1f12fc95b1135f20","tid":301433,"uid":71458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>密碼係個心</blockquote><br />\n比你講咗先"},{"pid":"a4e09fabae78f462220e4b9ec9e11cf2afd25b10","tid":301433,"uid":53233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor